### JWT Claims (CafeCanvas-specific)
```sql
-- Helper functions available in DB:
get_tenant_id()   → UUID from JWT app_metadata
get_user_role()   → TEXT role from JWT app_metadata
```

### RLS Policy Template
```sql
CREATE POLICY "{table}_read" ON {table}
  FOR SELECT TO authenticated
  USING (tenant_id = get_tenant_id());

CREATE POLICY "{table}_write" ON {table}
  FOR INSERT TO authenticated
  WITH CHECK (
    tenant_id = get_tenant_id()
    AND get_user_role() IN ('owner','manager')
  );
```

